{
  "id": "adv_event_2306_01_04",
  "title": "最高の一曲",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk001.m4a",
      "text": "結局、麻奈ちゃんがいなくなって\n約束していたライブは出来なかったんだけどね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In the end‚ we couldn't hold the promised live\nwithout Mana-chan.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "endTime": 7.368979549500001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-ktn001.m4a",
      "text": "そんなことがあったんですね\nじゃあ、私達に歌ってほしい曲って……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "So‚ that's what happened.\nThen‚ the song you want us to sing…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 7.5666666667,
      "endTime": 14.3000003179,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk002.m4a",
      "text": "あの時、私と麻奈ちゃんで歌うはずだった曲よ\nこの歌で麻奈ちゃんの想いも伝えたいの……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's supposed to be a song Mana-chan and I would sing together.\nI want to convey her feelings with this song too…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.4843557674,
      "endTime": 22.514741070899998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk003.m4a",
      "text": "麻奈ちゃんも星見プロの大切な仲間だから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because Mana-chan is also an important member of Hoshimi Prods.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 22.7176891008,
      "endTime": 26.2448764959,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-skr001.m4a",
      "text": "……私、歌いたい\nみんなで歌って、麻奈さんの想いも届けよう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I want to sing.\nLet's all sing together and deliver Mana-san's feelings!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.4510216712,
      "endTime": 32.8237426756,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-ktn002.m4a",
      "text": "そうね。遙子さん、私達にその曲を歌わせて下さい",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That's right. Haruko-san‚ please let us sing that song.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0176883379,
      "endTime": 38.666666921,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk004.m4a",
      "text": "さくらちゃん、琴乃ちゃん……ありがとう……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Sakura-chan‚ Kotono-chan… Thank you…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.846212705,
      "endTime": 43.6173693021,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-skr002.m4a",
      "text": "莉央ちゃんと瑠依ちゃん、それとfranさんにも\n新曲のことを伝えておかないとだね！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "We also need to inform Rio-chan‚ Ruri-chan‚\nand fran-san about the new song!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.8128793717,
      "endTime": 50.3756457329,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-ktn003.m4a",
      "text": "出来れば五人で集まって練習もしておきたいですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'd like the five of us to get together and practice if possible.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 50.5795460384,
      "endTime": 55.1273025195,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk005.m4a",
      "text": "それなら私に任せて。{user}君に\n内緒でスケジュールを組んでおくから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "In that case‚ leave it to me.\nI'll secretly arrange the schedule with {user}.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.3249896367,
      "endTime": 61.3921777089,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk006.m4a",
      "text": "星見プロ所属のアイドル二十人……いえ、二十一人で\n力を合わせて、最高のライブにしましょう！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "With the twenty idols of Hoshimi Prods… No‚ twenty-one idols‚\nlet's all work together to make the best live!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 61.5916563034,
      "endTime": 70,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――数日後",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――A few days later",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 71.0916522344,
      "endTime": 71.9819249868,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "skr",
      "speakerName": "川咲さくら",
      "speakerNameEn": "Sakura",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-sakura.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-skr003.m4a",
      "text": "いよいよ今日から新曲の練習開始だね\nドキドキしてきたよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Finally‚ today marks the start of practicing the new song.\nI'm getting nervous~.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 73.0583194097,
      "endTime": 78.92231047950001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-ktn004.m4a",
      "text": "このメンバーがどう混ざり合うのか……楽しみだね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It'll be interesting to see how this group mixes…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.1249860764,
      "endTime": 83.50434465410001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk007.m4a",
      "text": "みんな気合いは十分みたいね\n時間もないし早速始めましょうか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It seems everyone's motivated enough.\nWe don't have much time‚ so shall we start right away?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 83.7020317714,
      "endTime": 89.42765518830001,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rui",
      "speakerName": "天動瑠依",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rui",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rui.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-rui001.m4a",
      "text": "ちょっと待って。まだ一人来てないみたいだけど",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hold on a moment. Looks like one person hasn't arrived yet.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 89.6353651047,
      "endTime": 93.1530541421,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk008.m4a",
      "text": "franさんなら伝言で、「気が向いたら行くわ\n本番ではちゃんと合わせるから心配しないで」だそうよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "fran-san left a message saying‚ \"I'll go if I feel like it.\nDon't worry‚ I'll make sure to be there for the actual performance.\"",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 93.3507412594,
      "endTime": 102.0303770703,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rio",
      "speakerName": "神崎莉央",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rio",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rio.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-rio001.m4a",
      "text": "彼女らしいわね……\nまぁいいわ。さっさと始めるわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Typical of her…\nWell‚ let's just get started already.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 102.2174069088,
      "endTime": 106.949878661,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 7144.905050399999
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 108.2007402421
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "みんな、お疲れ様。差し入れを持って来たわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Everyone‚ good work. I brought some snacks.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 109.2507402421,
      "endTime": 114.17897862589999,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 114.4840776445
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "差し入れはなんだと思う？　芽衣が持って来た\n差し入れは……じゃーん！　ドーナツでしたー！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Guess what the snacks are? Mei broght them.\nsnacks are… Ta-da! Donuts!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.4840776445,
      "endTime": 124.9456452925,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-03.m4a",
          "delay": 1666.6625976999967
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 119.8633500654
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 125.2039880437
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣の差し入れは大抵ドーナツでしょ\nクイズにもならないわよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Mei's snacks are usually donuts.\nNot much of a quiz.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 125.2039880437,
      "endTime": 130.8789786259,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ktn",
      "speakerName": "長瀬琴乃",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kotono",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kotono.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-ktn005.m4a",
      "text": "でもなんだか懐かしいわ。デビュー前はよく\nレッスンの帰りにドーナツを買って食べたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "But it's kind of nostalgic. Before our debut‚\nwe often got donuts after lessons.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 131.1373330755,
      "endTime": 138.42135420149998,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 131.1373330755
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 138.6977805458
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "speakerNameEn": "Mei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "そうそう、月ストのみんなでドーナツを食べながら\n寮まで歩いて帰ったなぁ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Yeah‚ we used to walk back to the dormitory\neating donuts with everyone from Moon Tempest.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 138.6977805458,
      "endTime": 145.6917252063,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "レッスンの帰りなら、サニピは石焼き芋を\nみんなで買って食べたことがあったわね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After lessons‚ Sunny Peace used to buy roasted potatoes\nand eat them together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 145.9412962917,
      "endTime": 152.9088244441,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 153.1079629584
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "hrk",
      "speakerName": "佐伯遙子",
      "speakerNameEn": "Haruko",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-haruko.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/eventStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04/sud_vo_adv_event_2306_01_04-hrk009.m4a",
      "text": "それから、寒い日はコンビニで肉まんを買って……\nみんなで食べたわよね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "And on cold days‚ we'd buy meat buns from the convenience store\nand eat them together.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 153.1079629584,
      "endTime": 160.7370330497,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
          "delay": 9833.348592099981
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_dancestudiocorridor-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "dancestudiocorridor-00-noon",
      "startTime": 161.8246352199
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "chs",
      "speakerName": "白石千紗",
